summary:
Simone adds vision, focus, structure and delivery strength to the team, making sure to deliver to promises and putting the client at the center of her activities. 
She focuses on an end-to-end view of what needs to happen and will make sure things get done together with the team she is heading. She manages in an open and transparent manner, which means "I do what I say, say what I do". 

Industries of expertise:
Payments Industry
(Mobile) Telecommunications 
ICT Finance/Banking

Specialties: 
Product Management/ Product Development
Operations Management 
General Management
Chain and Process management
